high_descs: Turn around to walk to the end of the passage and turn right to reach the white diningtable.
Pick up the yellow mango from the table.
Turn around to walk to the end of the room, turn left to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the fridge.
Cool the mango in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left and walk down the passage to reach the white diningtable.
Put the mango on the diningtable behind the banana.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled mango on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn all the way around and go into the room at the end of the hall and take a right to the diningtable near the two chairs.
Pick up the mango with a pointy tip and the popsicle stick in it.
Turn around and leave the room and then walk down the hallway and go on your second left Into the kitchen to the fridge.
Put the mango in the refrigerator and then take it out.
Turn left and then right and go in to the diningtable at the end of the hall.
Put the mango on the diningtable next to the right chair.
anns.task_desc: Put the mango on the diningtable next to a chair.

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards the window, then turn right and walk towards the coffee table.
Pick up the mango, in front of the bottle, from the coffee table.
Turn back and walk towards the shelf, then turn left and walk across the room then turn left and walk, again turn left and head to the fridge.
Put the mango into the down rack of the fridge and pick it up back.
Turn left and walk, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk towards the coffee table.
Put the mango, right side of the bottle, on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mango on the coffee table.
